data.description: Move-In ready single story home with wood laminate floors throughout. New HVAC in 2021. Located on a quiet cul-de-sac with inviting front porch and covered patio in back. Large living/dining room combo. The kitchen includes stainless stove, dishwasher, microwave and refrigerator, granite counters and a stylish  tile backsplash. The separate laundry room off the kitchen includes the washer and dryer. The large master bedroom is in the front and features a large walk-in closet, an additional closet with shelving and an ensuite bathroom. Two additional bathrooms share a full bath. The backyard is fenced with privacy overlooking a wooded area. 1 car garage. Property is offered "as is."
